Installation of vSphere Hypervisor 6.0 on 
GCI Network Services, OSS Debian jessie 8.0 amd64 workstation.

1. Register and download the VMware vSphere Hypervisor 6.0.


2. At VMware vSphere Hypervisor 6.0 Download Center page:


Component                               License key
---------------------------------------------------------------------
VMware vSphere Hypervisor 6 License     450CJ-6UL01-J8A81-09886-94M4H


