HARDWARE COMPATIBILITY
The latest version of VMware vSphere Hypervisor is based
on VMware ESXi 6.0 which is certified to run on a broad
range of 64-bit hardware.  Check the Hardware Compatibility
List to ensure that the server model you intend to use is
certified to run VMware ESXi 6.0.


